org.drip.spaces.rxtord

Class NormedRxToNormedRd

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.drip.spaces.rxtord.NormedRxToNormedRd
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    NormedR1ToNormedRd, NormedRdToNormedRd

    public abstract class NormedRxToNormedRd
extends java.lang.Object
    NormedRxToNormedRd is the abstract Class that exposes f : Normed R^x (x .gte. 1) To Normed R^d Function Space. The Reference we've used is: - Carl, B., and I. Stephani (1990): Entropy, Compactness, and Approximation of Operators, Cambridge University Press, Cambridge UK.
    Author:
    Lakshmi Krishnamurthy
